description:
WED 9/21 - The Breakfast Club discusses The Game's habit of kissing & telling after he alluded to the 3 Kardashian girls he slept with. Is that fair or foul? Then a caller tells on herself after giving a guy herpes during "Ask Yee". The reaction from the club might make her wish STD stood for Stop Telling Dirt.....
